- if I am a minor unaccompanied by my parents and supported by child welfare <bold>(ASE)</bold>;
- if I have a declared job in France;
- if I am joining my family for reunification or family reunification;
- if I am a student;
- if I am an asylum seeker and have been in France for more than three months; 
- if I have been living in France for more than three months.

- my identity and those of the other persons (children, spouses) for whom the request is made;
- of my stable, uninterrupted and irregular presence with regard to the right of residence on French territory since at least least three months;
- to have resources below the ceiling determined by decree.
